title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E97 - Taryon My Wayward Son
description: Brian Wayne Foster is joined by Taliesin Jaffe, Matthew Mercer, Sam Riegel, and Keyleth in fish form for Talks Machina! They discuss Critical Role episode 97, Keyleth's graceful landing, and give out prizes!
